The developers sincerely would like to implement alot of the great ideas players come up with.  More often then not it's a limitation of time or computer resources to do so however.  How do I know this?  Because I've heard them speak in person at an EQ fan fair.  They are not the demons many players make them out to be.  Most players make suggestions with out really thinking about &quot;the big picture&quot;.<br>
